thread.title: BRIEF-Resilient Reit Sees 13 Pct Higher Dividend For FY Ended June 2018

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Resilient Reit Sees 13 Pct Higher Dividend For FY Ended June 2018
text:
Jan 11 (Reuters) - Resilient Reit Ltd:
* RESILIENT REIT LTD - ANTICIPATES THAT DIVIDEND PER SHARE FOR INTERIM PERIOD ENDED 31 DECEMBER 2017 WILL BE BETWEEN 305.35 CENTS AND 306.70 CENTS
* RESILIENT REIT LTD - TRADING IN CURRENT FINANCIAL YEAR HAS BEEN CONSISTENT WITH PROSPECTS PREVIOUSLY COMMUNICATED
* RESILIENT REIT - CONFIRMS THAT DIVIDEND FOR FINANCIAL YEAR ENDING 30 JUNE 2018 IS ANTICIPATED TO INCREASE BY APPROXIMATELY 13%, AS PREVIOUSLY GUIDED Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
